	"data": "<div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَلَا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> تَقۡرَبُواْ مَالَ ٱلۡيَتِيمِ إِلَّا بِٱلَّتِي هِيَ أَحۡسَنُ حَتَّىٰ </div><div><a data-content='استحكام قوّته ويرشد' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>يَبۡلُغَ أَشُدَّهُۥۚ</a></div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَأَوۡفُواْ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٱلۡكَيۡلَ وَٱلۡمِيزَانَ <a data-content='بالعدل دون زيادة ونقص' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>بِٱلۡقِسۡطِۖ</a> لَا نُكَلِّفُ نَفۡسًا </div><div>إِلَّا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div><a data-content='طاقتها وما تقدِر عليه' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>وُسۡعَهَاۖ</a> وَإِذَا قُلۡتُمۡ فَٱعۡدِلُواْ وَلَوۡ كَانَ ذَا قُرۡبَىٰۖ وَبِعَهۡدِ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'></div><div>وَبِعَهۡدِ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱللَّهِ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> أَوۡفُواْۚ ذَٰلِكُمۡ وَصَّىٰكُم بِهِۦ لَعَلَّكُمۡ تَذَكَّرُونَ </div><div>١٥٢</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَأَنَّ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> هَٰذَا <a data-content='سبيلي وديني لا اعوجاج فيه' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>صِرَٰطِي مُسۡتَقِيمٗا</a> فَٱتَّبِعُوهُۖ وَلَا تَتَّبِعُواْ </div><div>ٱلسُّبُلَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>فَتَفَرَّقَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> بِكُمۡ عَن سَبِيلِهِۦۚ ذَٰلِكُمۡ وَصَّىٰكُم بِهِۦ </div><div>لَعَلَّكُمۡ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>تَتَّقُونَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ١٥٣ ثُمَّ ءَاتَيۡنَا مُوسَى ٱلۡكِتَٰبَ تَمَامًا عَلَى </div><div>ٱلَّذِيٓ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>أَحۡسَنَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَتَفۡصِيلٗا لِّكُلِّ شَيۡءٖ وَهُدٗى وَرَحۡمَةٗ لَّعَلَّهُم </div><div>بِلِقَآءِ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>رَبِّهِمۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> يُؤۡمِنُونَ ١٥٤ وَهَٰذَا كِتَٰبٌ أَنزَلۡنَٰهُ مُبَارَكٞ </div><div>فَٱتَّبِعُوهُ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَٱتَّقُواْ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> لَعَلَّكُمۡ تُرۡحَمُونَ ١٥٥ أَن تَقُولُوٓاْ إِنَّمَآ أُنزِلَ </div><div>ٱلۡكِتَٰبُ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>عَلَىٰ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> طَآئِفَتَيۡنِ مِن قَبۡلِنَا وَإِن كُنَّا عَن دِرَاسَتِهِمۡ </div><div>لَغَٰفِلِينَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>١٥٦</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> أَوۡ تَقُولُواْ لَوۡ أَنَّآ أُنزِلَ عَلَيۡنَا ٱلۡكِتَٰبُ لَكُنَّآ </div><div>أَهۡدَىٰ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>مِنۡهُمۡۚ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> فَقَدۡ جَآءَكُم بَيِّنَةٞ مِّن رَّبِّكُمۡ وَهُدٗى </div><div>وَرَحۡمَةٞۚ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>فَمَنۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> أَظۡلَمُ مِمَّن كَذَّبَ بِ‍َٔايَٰتِ ٱللَّهِ <a data-content='أعرض عنها أو صرف 